text: Hanli Hoefer is a Singaporean of German and Peranakan descent, Singapore-based VJ for MTV Asia. She started her career as a model at Ave Management and became the MTV VJ in 2013 to current. ==References== Category:Singaporean television presenters Category: Singaporean people of German descent Category: Singaporean people of Peranakan descent Category:1992 births Category:Living people
